Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:12.14,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur5\pos(813.467,303.534)}{\fs32}wanderer
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵船展示了其全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焕发出黄金的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王族的夙愿…政治纷争…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分处茉莉香敌友位置的两位公主 最终能和解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而身为船长 茉莉香所想到的策略到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 猛烈宇宙海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:23:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自永恒回归
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:23:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
